{"tid":2348871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"河北拘禁教廷駐港兩修女  京圖取締外交使團 干預主教任命","createTime":"2021-01-01T05:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T06:44:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d27a040479c7f8f957d675f17eb43d5f7778ead","tid":2348871,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210101/FLHPOOFG6BE3RJD2KEU3WALYB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210101%2FFLHPOOFG6BE3RJD2KEU3WALYB4%2F&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=6935078f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210101%2FFLHPOOFG6BE3RJD2KEU3WALYB4%2F&h=90f13a92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210101/FLHPOOFG6BE3RJD2KEU3WALYB4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n河北拘禁教廷駐港兩修女 <br />\n京圖取締外交使團 干預主教任命<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中國不斷打壓香港自由消除異已，天主教香港教區也成目標。路透社偵查報道指，兩名於梵蒂岡在港設立的非正式外交使團工作的修女，返河北探親時被捕，遭軟禁及監視多月。有神職人員認為北京的行動展示了對外交使團在港工作的不滿，北京或意圖取締該使團，並擴大對香港教區的控制，包括介入下任主教任命。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：湯漢刪「失蹤」大陸主教內容<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述三名知情神職人員指，兩名被捕修女均40多歲，來自中國，在外交使團侍奉已五年，去年5月返回河北家鄉時被關押三周，之後在未被起訴下於寓所繼續軟禁及受監視，至上月才取消軟禁，但不得離開中國。<br />\n<br />\n有與中國溝通多年的神職人員指，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LpZ8lfpsDJCcYtWMKUyEJFp04po=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/254BF7J7C5B5NHKCX34STQTKA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLpZ8lfpsDJCcYtWMKUyEJFp04po%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F254BF7J7C5B5NHKCX34STQTKA4.jpg&h=3976b70d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中共嚴格管制內地宗教事務，有信徒將習近平如上帝般供奉。 互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n使團為梵蒂岡在華唯一前哨站<br />\n<br />\n路透社指該使團設於「九龍市郊」一獨立屋內，由於中國與梵蒂岡沒有邦交，成梵蒂岡在不包括台灣的中國境內唯一政治前哨站，地位敏感下非常低調，使團的資料不列入香港教區通訊錄內。領導使團的兩名代辦在北京和香港都沒有正式地位，也不會見香港官員，但會跟本港和中國的神職人員和機構維持聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n路透社形容，隨着北京在港訂立。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i7wC0jC4Y_X7s8pmUh_ptQFVOfc=/1832x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XYYJUIPDB5HWDCA4UCPASQTA2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi7wC0jC4Y_X7s8pmUh_ptQFVOfc%3D%2F1832x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXYYJUIPDB5HWDCA4UCPASQTA2I.jpg&h=4d85dab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■中梵早前續簽主教任命協議，教宗方濟各被指縱容北京打壓中國教區。<br />\n<br />\n不過梵蒂岡人員指，因香港是特別行政區，。。。。。，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君樞機回應路透社訪問時指：「我們已在井底&mdash;&mdash;不再有言論自由。這些情況在中國是常態，如今我們已變成中國另一個市。」。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社指特首林鄭月娥書面回應查詢時，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"6054d5ce8cb58d904b7c65ff536c2c2f57a76d7c","tid":2348871,"uid":289292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"教宗玩緊Ig唔得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0aa5353083240f7550881db479b8472bd86095a","tid":2348871,"uid":282347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6054d5ce8cb58d904b7c65ff536c2c2f57a76d7c","tid":2348871,"uid":289292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"教宗玩緊Ig唔得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:13:56.000Z","msg":"同緊biden研究幻幻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5982809fa4a4d795516d163a00754187a273b17a","tid":2348871,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6054d5ce8cb58d904b7c65ff536c2c2f57a76d7c","tid":2348871,"uid":289292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"教宗玩緊Ig唔得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":